reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fantastic Desk! Perfect for Gamers and Artists!
reviews.reviewText: Bought this desk so I could have a more cohesive digital art setup and it is AMAZING. Plenty of leg room, easy to assemble, and is very high quality for the price! The only warning / downside is that this desk is heavy and comes in a very heavy box. I had to open it and transport pieces one by one upstairs. If you're unable to carry or have someone help with the box, be prepared for how heavy it is! But the upside is a great sturdy desk that is the new star of the office setup I have!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It's a nice and sturdy computer desk.
reviews.reviewText: I like the way you can set it up, in different designs. I like the drawers to store other things.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Incredible value and quality!
reviews.reviewText: I rarely write reviews, but this product and seller warrants one. This desk is incredible, especially at this price. It took awhile to assemble, but what shipped furniture doesn’t? It came with all the tools needed as well. It shipped in the original box which had some damage on the outside, but none of the wood was broken or scratched at all. The file frame for the bottom drawer was broken, however. I emailed the seller who responded promptly, asked for photos, confirmed the part, and shipped out a new one. If I don’t receive it, I’ll update this review, but I can live without it at this price point. They were very easy to work with and responsive. Highly recommend this product and seller!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars An all-around great desk
reviews.reviewText: I'd give this desk five stars if the assembly hadn't been so time-consuming and tedious (though the instructions were excellent). Definitely hire someone (or get a friend to help you) if you're not accustomed to assembling fairly complex items. That said, I really like this desk. It looks modern, it's sturdy, the drawers provide plenty of storage, and the power outlet feature is a great addition.

I was worried when I read the instructions and it did not illustrate the configuration that I wanted (the L-shape), but it was easy to put in that shape so it's all good. When assembling, I would recommend mounting the power strip so that the ground pins arefacing the back ofthe desk, otherwise the USB cable for the LEDs will be a bit short. The storage space is impressive. Is it as sturdy as the hundred year old typewriter desk it replaced? no, but nothing will be unless you want to pay over $1000.

I have many good things to say about this desk. Assembled it by myself, which took a while but wasn’t hard. Everything fit perfectly, all the components were organized and labelled, they included extra pieces of everything, and it came with the tools you need, too. The instructions were very detailed and simple to follow. This desk is perfect for my work/study station which needed an L-shaped desk with enough space for my printer, laptop, ipad, desktop, and my books. The power bar is also very useful - it comes with 4 outlets, 2 usb-a ports (one is for the LED lights if you want them on), and 1 usb-c port. I only wish the drawer handles weren’t plastic because they look and feel very cheap, but once you screw them in, they are sturdy and blend into the black finish so it doesn’t really matter.Edit: I have a slight complaint that the finish is very prone to fingerprints but otherwise, it’s a great desk and worth the money!

Ce meuble de bureau est le meilleur que j'ai eu. Il est super facile à assembler, robuste et bien conçu, il suffit de suivre les étapes clairement indiquées sur le plan.La boîte est très lourde et je m'attendais à ce qu'il y ait eu des dommages durant le transport mais non, l'entreprise qui a fabriqué le meuble à pris soins de très bien le protégée à l'intérieur de la boîte et il est arrivé en parfait état.Ce meuble est tellement complet, un classeur pour mettre mes documents, des tiroirs pour ranger mes choses de bureau, un endroit pour mettre un imprimante, deux espaces de rangement tablette, un tiroir tablette pour mettre un clavier et une souris et un espace de travail très grand et dégager pour étalé mes documents pendant que je travaille sur l'ordinateur sans être encombré, enfin, que demander de plus.Je le recommande fortement parce qu'il est complet et satisfait toute mes attentes en termes de conception et d'efficacité.
